  "title": "Admin / Sales Operations Assistant (Jurong East)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location: Jurong East</strong></p><p><strong>Working hours: 8am to 5pm (Monday to Friday), 8am to 12pm (alternate Saturdays off)</strong></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Perform general administrative tasks: typing, filing, faxing, and record-keeping.</li><li>Assist in sales operations, including preparing quotations, invoices, and other sales documents.</li><li>Support logistics and documentation processes for deliveries and fleet coordination.</li><li>Maintain customer databases and update records accurately.</li><li>Liaise with internal teams, suppliers, and customers to ensure smooth workflow.</li><li>Handle ad-hoc administrative and operational tasks as assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>ITE/ Diploma.</li><li>Training is provided.</li><li>Good organizational, typing, and communication skills.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, Outlook).</li><li>Detail-oriented and able to manage multiple tasks efficiently.</li><li>Positive attitude, proactive, and willing to learn.</li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:lilian@juhlerprofessionals.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">lilian@juhlerprofessionals.com.sg</a></p><p>Tan Li Lian</p><p>EA 01C3135</p><p>Reg R1100465</p>",
